Text: Re CONFIDENTIAL Enron Sun Devil Term sheetGot it Thanks Talk to you by Friday Aloha Hyatt Kevin To KevinHyatt cc Lindberg Lorraine enroncom Subject CONFIDENTIAL Enron Sun Devil Term sheet PM Russ Attached for your review is the confidential proposed Term Sheet for Transwesterns Sun Devil Project As we discussed it includes a swing capability for Duke within a hour period plus delivery capability to Cal Border After youve had a chance to review please call me and we can address any questions you may have I look forward to hearing from you later this week Hope you are enjoying the snow Best Regards Kevin Hyatt Duke termsheetdoc This email is the property of Enron Corp andor its relevant affiliate and may contain confidential and privileged material for the sole use of the intended recipient s Any review use distribution or disclosure by others is strictly prohibited If you are not the intended recipient or authorized to receive for the recipient please contact the sender or reply to Enron Corp at and delete all copies of the message This email and any attachments hereto are not intended to be an offer or an acceptance and do not create or evidence a binding and enforceable contract between Enron Corp or any of its affiliates and the intended recipient or any other party and may not be relied on by anyone as the basis of a contract by estoppel or otherwise Thank you See attached file Duke termsheetdoc
